### 新增 Modbus RTU 設備
POST {{host}}/api/devices HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "name": "RTU_DEVICE",
  "protocol": "modbus_rtu",
  "com": "/dev/ttyUSB0",
  "baudrate": 9600,
  "databits": 8,
