### 更新虛擬點位
PUT {{host}}/api/points/4c3cd3e5-17ff-4b73-bee1-4613cabc561a HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新的點位名稱",
  "description": "已更新的虛擬點位",
  "datatype": "float",
  "initvalue": 10.5,
  "opt": "NONE",
  "savetype": "temp",
  "enable": true,
  "correctionvalue": 1.0,
  "ptuuids": []
}

### 刪除虛擬點位
DELETE {{host}}/api/points/06bc1d2b-97ec-44c6-b907-a8a4a850465e HTTP/1.1

